{"tid":2275211,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"六旬漢不滿收樓縱火 執達吏稱警方跑光 由佢協助疏散市民","createTime":"2020-11-07T03:52:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T05:47:32.000Z","uid":123774,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ce7b69badf64adef2aecabae5d344dc76c07efbe","tid":2275211,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T03:52:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201106/IVIZOEMTQ5AL5FU5SLT7SI7EUM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201106%2FIVIZOEMTQ5AL5FU5SLT7SI7EUM%2F&d=J7URIij%2BjV7QbFiEH5rjuIT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=2f533d46\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201106%2FIVIZOEMTQ5AL5FU5SLT7SI7EUM%2F&h=ed4a5f40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201106/IVIZOEMTQ5AL5FU5SLT7SI7EUM/</a><br />\n<br />\n家住將軍澳居屋的六旬漢拖欠管理費多年，因而遭執達吏上門收回住所。六旬漢涉在收樓當天從住所向走廊掟出燃燒物，導致發生爆炸，他則經單位外水管爬到樓下單位逃走，最終在梯間被消防及警員發現。六旬漢聲言事先購入天拿水及石油氣罐，以圖與執達吏「一鑊熟」，並於案發當天劈爛石油氣罐以放火。他面對一項有意圖而縱火罪，今在高等法院受審。據在場執達吏供稱，當日於火警現場的警員跑光，本打算逃生的他於是協助疏散住客。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w3g10qC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw3g10qC.jpg&h=fdb8ad47&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8625e62d0d83f60cfcb4ed39f369e19b34da787","tid":2275211,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T03:57:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f761d53b6ccd51a7322265773252acfb3e7c7b36","tid":2275211,"uid":167007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T05:10:58.000Z","msg":"平時練既體能幾有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a3cb42be734dabeea9b200e18f0dc566f3411e6","tid":2275211,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T05:47:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}